TITLE: Implementing MCP Session Logic in Python
DESCRIPTION: Python class definition for an MCP `Session`, inheriting from `BaseSession`. It provides asynchronous methods for sending requests (`send_request`), sending notifications (`send_notification`), and handling received requests (`_received_request`) and notifications (`_received_notification`), forming the basis for Python MCP implementations.
