TITLE: Defining Tool-Related Schemas
DESCRIPTION: Defines schemas for tools, tool listing, and tool invocation in the protocol. These schemas validate the structure of tool-related requests and responses between client and server.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master/blob/main/context/mcp-js-sdk-docs.txt#2025-04-23_snippet_212

