TITLE: Implementing a New Feature Core Function in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Provides a concrete example of implementing a new feature (`newFeature`) within a core module (`task-manager.js`). It follows the established pattern, using `options.source` to control UI visibility and return values (structured object for MCP, console output for CLI), and includes source-specific error handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master/blob/main/context/MCP_INTEGRATION.md#2025-04-23_snippet_2

