TITLE: Testing Prompt Argument Completion in MCP Server
DESCRIPTION: Test that verifies prompt argument completion functionality where the server provides completion suggestions for partial argument values. The server defines a custom completion handler for the 'name' argument of a 'countryPoem' prompt.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master/blob/main/context/fastmcp-docs.txt#2025-04-23_snippet_32

