TITLE: URI Template Implementation Class
DESCRIPTION: Core implementation of the UriTemplate class with RFC 6570 compliant parsing and expansion capabilities. Includes validation and security measures.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master/blob/main/context/mcp-js-sdk-docs.txt#2025-04-23_snippet_184

