TITLE: Testing Process Cleanup with Jest in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: A Jest test that verifies servers properly clean up resources after transport closure. The test creates a server instance with a StdioServerTransport, closes the transport, and ensures the process exits cleanly without hanging.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master/blob/main/context/mcp-js-sdk-docs.txt#2025-04-23_snippet_53

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
