TITLE: Passing SessionID to Tool Callback
DESCRIPTION: Tests that the sessionId is correctly passed to tool callbacks via the RequestHandlerExtra parameter. This confirms the tool can access session-specific context when handling requests.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master/blob/main/context/mcp-js-sdk-docs.txt#2025-04-23_snippet_120

